playthrough <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849140/extras/5fa5093c1e75a11df60e7c2afaea0bb4.webp?t=1624625877\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Light resource management combines with an inventory and relationship system to let you feel the weight of every decision you make<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849140/extras/5fa5093c1e75a11df60e7c2afaea0bb4.webp?t=1624625877\" width=16 height=16 /></span> More than 30 random events combine with the main narrative arc to let you experience something new each time you steep in the world of Midnight Caravan",
